do Variables.add_local("sacrifice", false)
do Variables.add_local("dream", false)
=> start

~ start
You wake up feeling dizzy. You get out of bed and make your way to the main room. Once there, you take your place behind the work station. You look around for a bit before you start hearing heavy footsteps coming down the stairs.
Shopkeeper: Morning, there. I see you're itching to get started. Sleep well?
- Morning. Slept just fine. 
